      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Eirik commands 8 Chainwardens at a fortified toll checkpoint with good sightlines and defensive positions. Threatening or intimidating him is catastrophic&mdash;&minus;2 Patience. If Patience reaches 0, the party is detained.</p>",
          "director": "<p>Do not let the PCs fight their way through Greypass. Eight wardens behind fortifications is not a winnable encounter at this level. The negotiation is the encounter.</p>"
