    {
      "name": "Road Intelligence",
      "type": "feature",
      "_id": "ERGR000000000003",
      "img": "icons/sundries/scrolls/scroll-runed-tan-white.webp",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>If Interest is achieved, Eirik provides free passage and road intelligence: 'Mountain road passable but ugly; two rockfalls; gorge bridge unstable; large tracks in high country&mdash;something that walks on two legs but drags something behind it.' Good negotiation with Eirik also provides an edge on later Chainwarden patrol encounters.</p>",
          "director": "<p>The 'large tracks' hint at the Bone Fields and the larger draugr threat. Don't explain this&mdash;just let it unsettle.</p>"
        },
